---
title: Creamy Middle Eastern Cauliflower Tagine with Couscous & Spiced Tomato Sauce
description: A tagine is traditionally a slow-cooked Moroccan dish, bursting with flavour and delightful aromas. Well, we've kept the flavour and fragrance, but made it speedier for you to enjoy sooner. Bask in a combination of fluffy couscous, roasted pumpkin, sweetly spiced tomato sauce and a smattering of almonds and you too will think of a tagine as a surprising weeknight staple.
